      <para id="ExponentialProperties">
	The properties of the exponential make calculating the product and ratio of two complex numbers much simpler when the numbers are expressed in polar form.
	<equation id="eq16">
	  <m:math>
	    <m:apply>
	      <m:eq/>
	      <m:apply>
